edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.shuffletter.iface

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.shuffletter.iface.Position

  • public class Position
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing positions on the playing grid. Because the playing grid extends arbitrarily in any direction, negative coordinates are admissible. The X and Y coordinates for a Position are oriented in the same fashion as a Cartesian coordinate plane: increasing X moves to the right while increasing Y moves upward.
